description: The iBoxx Euro Germany 1-3 Total Return Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: EUR-denominated bonds issued by the German government Bonds with maturities between 1 and 3 years Minimum amount outstanding of EUR 1 billion per bond Additional information on the Index and the general methodology behind the Markit iBoxx indices can be found on Markit iBoxx website ( https://www.markit.com ).
name: Xtrackers II Germany Government Bond 1-3 UCITS ETF 1D
